  "page_title": "SMC_SetMovementType (FB)",
  "text": "\nFUNCTION_BLOCK SMC_SetMovementType\nSets the movement type of a virtual axis to linear or modulo.\nCan only be used when the axis is in state\nstandstill\nor\npower_off\n.\nThe FB executes synchronously on the rising edge of\nbExecute\n.\nAfter the call, either\nbDone\nor\nbError\nare set.\n",
